171 A.3d 1263 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. MICHAEL RICHARD POWERS, DEFENDANT.

C-213 Sept.Term 2017

078794 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003764-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
